    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) is one gradation below the required level due to the single test configuration, which is acknowledged as a limitation but does not invalidate the overall assessment given the high consistency across N=11 constructs and two laboratories. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; relative error < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as sufficiently credible for the stated COU. NOTE FOR WEAKENER DETECTION: All ValidationResults in this package were generated by ModelConfiguration ansys-mech-2024q3-build-2 (modelVersion: 2024-q3-build-2), while the UnitOfAssurance declares currentModelVersion: 2026-q1-build-7. The supporting evidence therefore applies to a prior model build and does not demonstrate credibility of the current model of record.",
